<L>To naval union. Trent and Severn's wave,</L>
<L><PB N="86" REF="89">
By plains alone di&s;parted, woo to join</L>
<L>Maje&s;tic Thamis. With their &s;ilver urns</L>
<L>The nimble-footed Naiads of the &s;prings</L>
