<L>Long &s;itting at the loom; and tho&s;e be&s;ides,</L>
<L>Who crown, with yellow &s;heaves, the farmer's hopes$</L>
<L>And all the genii of commercial toil:</L>
<L>The&s;e on the dewy lawns await, to &s;peed</L>
