<L>To great Augu&s;ta's mart, where lofty trade,</L>
<L>Amid a thou&s;and golden &s;pires enthron'd,</L>
<L>Gives audience to the world: the &s;trand around</L>
<L N="630">Clo&s;e &s;warms with bu&s;y crouds of many a realm.</L>
